page.title: 11SPILSBY CARNIVAL
page.content: Dad made me up first.He used make-up. He gave me a black eye,red freckles and a scar.Mum gave me two black teeth.My outfit was Dads old shirt jeans and jumper.They were all cut up and holy.When I reached Spilsby I dimbed on my float.It was really lorry with a big boot made out of sacks on the back.We all peeped out of the windows exept for the six people sitting on chairs outside.Soon we were off driving very slowly round the town.My back was stiff and my legs were aching,but I kept on waving and smiling at everybody.Soon we heard the results.We came fourth. We had to ride around the town again.My Mum,Dad and my brother,Edward took two photographs of me.
